sequenceDiagram
  actor Roco as Roco (admin)
  participant Ed as PlanEditor
  participant DB as Supabase
  participant Bot as btrt-bot
  actor Mem as Miembro

  Roco->>Ed: arma la semana (tipos, horarios, niveles)
  Ed->>DB: saveWeek -> weeks.plan (JSONB)
  Ed->>Bot: POST /notify (Bearer JWT)
  Bot->>Bot: verifica que el email sea admin
  Bot-->>Mem: web-push "Planificacion disponible"
  Note over Mem: aunque la app este cerrada (PWA)
  Mem->>DB: loadWeek (lee el plan publicado)
  Mem->>DB: toggle turno -> week_attendance
  Mem->>DB: week_roster RPC (ve quien mas va)
